        <h1>aiSummerizer Support</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Get help with recording, transcribing, and organizing your meetings</p>

        <div class="contact-box">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Need Help?</h3>
            <p>If you can't find the answer to your question below, please contact us:</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:golukicoding@gmail.com">golukicoding@gmail.com</a></p>
